{"tid":870721,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【冇得擔心】傳徐濠縈陪女康堤到外國升學 陳奕迅：唔係咁益我呀","createTime":"2018-10-21T10:47:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T05:43:01.000Z","uid":130626,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"1bfccb84b0b582ce893d2976e5f948635e8ad1f1","tid":870721,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T10:47:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181021/large/1540112446_b7e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181021%2Flarge%2F1540112446_b7e8.jpg&h=c8cd81d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳奕迅(Eason)今日到元朗出席按摩產品發佈會，下個禮拜六喺中環開騷嘅佢又明顯瘦咗，佢透露之前舊病復發令扁桃腺發炎，入咗醫院吊咗幾日鹽水同專心休息下，現時還有少少喉嚨痛及只能食白飯白粥，佢表示幸好並非開騷嗰個禮拜先病。<br />\n日前有指徐濠縈結束生意陪伴愛女康堤到外國升學，Eason鬼馬咁話：「唔係，冇提過，只係話隨時準備咁做，真係走咁正，我好耐未曾試過自己獨霸一間屋，唔係咁益我吓。」Eason表示一日未成事，都唔知會唔會掛住愛女，不過佢憶述自己留學時生活好忙，都冇時間掛住屋企，佢話：「睇下佢揀男女校定女校，如果係我揀就男女校，咁到時真係唔會掛住喇，青春期係咁㗎啦。」Eason表示冇得擔心，最緊要平衡到讀書同玩，佢又讚康堤好有交帶，平日好少帶朋友返屋企玩，問到唔帶男友返屋企會唔會仲擔心？佢開通咁話：「唔會，呢方面我哋好open，到適當嘅時候見到就見，冇乜所謂。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181021/58819259\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181021%2F58819259&d=9i0SjJOlFOBs6tAFn2eGcMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=5606f610\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181021%2F58819259&h=8c464678\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181021/58819259</a>"},{"pid":"9e60c98d4ab644299de8ea22778490cd0b86e852","tid":870721,"uid":58140,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T10:48:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a11b3b871800dd91c4f8abf0f5c017e6ec09ee5d","tid":870721,"uid":132587,"like":51,"dislike":